<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> That is not quite right. Whoever engages the mob first, not whoever was preparing or had the force in the zone etc...&quot;gets&quot; the mob. So kiting Lozidal is fine. It may suck for others, but it is better than the &quot;I CALLED IT FIRST&quot; fights that would be happening if the rule was otherwise.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
