<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> According to a member of my guild who was present from the start, when we engaged Lodizal Agema had perhaps 3 people in the area. This is why he was surprised that I would share loot.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
